{
  "stem": "13833.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--was the sixth-- he, [LAUGHS] he was the sixth secretary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when he first went to speak to these, then the ambassador said, Raoul, I think I should go and speak. because I am a diplomat.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And our Raoul laughed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, sir, you will be a dead talk as a diplomat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I will not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so he took over, really, the whole embassy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At first, they didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then our ambassador helped us a lot with that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Guts.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then he picked up the people because here, we had the houses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he put them in these safe houses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they're supposed to be safe in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--by, by this time, let's say, by September, we already had about 20,000 people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then we had another 10,000.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the problem was that none of us, and not him especially-- sleeping two, three hours a night because he had to go constantly now.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Eichmann decided that-- you see, before Raoul arrived, Eichmann was there three months before him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he killed 475,000 people in the country-- priests, nuns, Jews, people in the wheelchair, mentally retarded people, [NON-ENGLISH], and took them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So those who were in the country, those, those Jews were-- You just interviewed a Hungarian lady.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know who did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She just told me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was in the country, and she was taken to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the film crew was just out doing it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But she-- so Raoul had really no choice because then the bombing started, and going away from Hungary was impossible.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then there was a Polish gentleman who came in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he started to imitate these same things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He had a little printing machine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And Raoul found out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was very, very angry.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
